{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "00-public-auth-collection-v3",
		"name": "00 - Public & Auth (No Auth Required)",
		"description": "Public endpoints and authentication endpoints that don't require authentication.\n\n**Authentication Required**: No\n\n**Rate Limits**:\n- Login: 5 attempts / 15 minutes\n- Register: 10 / hour\n- Forgot Password: 3 / hour\n- Verify Email: 5 / hour\n\n**Base URL**: {{baseUrl}}/v1\n\n**Last Updated**: 15-03-26\n**Version**: 3.0 - Added OAuth endpoints (Google, Apple)",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:5000",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "accessToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "refreshToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "userId",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "googleIdToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "Google OAuth ID token for testing"
		},
		{
			"key": "appleIdentityToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "Apple Sign In identity token for testing"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "OAuth Authentication",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Google Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"accessToken\", jsonData.data.tokens.accessToken);",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"refreshToken\", jsonData.data.tokens.refreshToken);",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"userId\", jsonData.data.user._id);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@gmail.com\",\n  \"name\": \"Google User\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/google-login",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["v1", "auth", "google-login"]
						},
						"description": "Login with Google OAuth\n\n**Backend Route**: `POST /auth/google-login`\n\n**Flow**:\n1. User signs in with Google on frontend\n2. Frontend gets Google ID token\n3. Send token to backend\n4. Backend creates/updates user and returns tokens\n\n**Rate Limit**: 5 attempts per 15 minutes"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Google Login V2",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"accessToken\", jsonData.data.tokens.accessToken);",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"refreshToken\", jsonData.data.tokens.refreshToken);",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"userId\", jsonData.data.user._id);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@gmail.com\",\n  \"name\": \"Google User\",\n  \"avatar\": \"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/...\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/google-login/v2",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["v1", "auth", "google-login", "v2"]
						},
						"description": "Enhanced Google login with FCM token support\n\n**Backend Route**: `POST /auth/google-login/v2`\n\n**Rate Limit**: 5 attempts per 15 minutes"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Google OAuth Callback",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"idToken\": \"{{googleIdToken}}\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/google",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["v1", "auth", "google"]
						},
						"description": "Google OAuth callback endpoint\n\n**Backend Route**: `POST /auth/google`\n\n**Flow**:\n1. Frontend receives Google ID token after OAuth flow\n2. Send idToken to this endpoint\n3. Backend verifies token and authenticates user\n\n**Note**: Client sends idToken for verification"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Apple Sign In",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"identityToken\": \"{{appleIdentityToken}}\",\n  \"name\": \"Apple User\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/apple",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["v1", "auth", "apple"]
						},
						"description": "Sign in with Apple\n\n**Backend Route**: `POST /auth/apple`\n\n**Flow**:\n1. User signs in with Apple on frontend\n2. Frontend gets identity token\n3. Send token to backend\n4. Backend verifies and authenticates user\n\n**Note**: Client sends identityToken for verification"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Health Check",
			"request": {
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [],
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/health",
					"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
					"path": ["v1", "health"]
				},
				"description": "Check API health status\n\n**Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"status\": \"healthy\",\n    \"db\": \"connected\",\n    \"redis\": \"connected\",\n    \"queues\": {\n      \"critical\": \"active\",\n      \"standard\": \"active\",\n      \"low\": \"active\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Note**: Health endpoint may not be implemented yet - verify with backend team"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Register User",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
							"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    pm.environment.set(\"userEmail\", jsonData.data.user.email);",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/register",
					"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
					"path": ["v1", "auth", "register"]
				},
				"description": "Register a new user account\n\n**Body**:\n- name: User's full name\n- email: Valid email address\n- password: Minimum 8 characters\n\n**Rate Limit**: 10 per hour\n\n**Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user\": {\n      \"_id\": \"...\",\n      \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n      \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n      \"role\": \"user\"\n    },\n    \"message\": \"OTP sent to your email\"\n  }\n}\n```"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Login",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
							"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    pm.environment.set(\"accessToken\", jsonData.data.tokens.accessToken);",
							"    pm.environment.set(\"refreshToken\", jsonData.data.tokens.refreshToken);",
							"    pm.environment.set(\"userId\", jsonData.data.user._id);",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/login",
					"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
					"path": ["v1", "auth", "login"]
				},
				"description": "Login with email and password\n\n**Rate Limit**: 5 attempts per 15 minutes\n\n**Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user\": {\n      \"_id\": \"...\",\n      \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n      \"email\": \"john@example.com\"\n    },\n    \"tokens\": {\n      \"accessToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\",\n      \"refreshToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Verify Email",
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/verify-email",
					"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
					"path": ["v1", "auth", "verify-email"]
				},
				"description": "Verify email with OTP\n\n**Rate Limit**: 5 per hour"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Resend OTP",
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/resend-otp",
					"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
					"path": ["v1", "auth", "resend-otp"]
				},
				"description": "Resend verification OTP\n\n**Rate Limit**: 5 per hour"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Forgot Password",
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/forgot-password",
					"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
					"path": ["v1", "auth", "forgot-password"]
				},
				"description": "Request password reset OTP\n\n**Rate Limit**: 3 per hour"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Reset Password",
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewSecurePass123!\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/reset-password",
					"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
					"path": ["v1", "auth", "reset-password"]
				},
				"description": "Reset password with OTP"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Refresh Token",
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/refresh-auth",
					"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
					"path": ["v1", "auth", "refresh-auth"]
				},
				"description": "Refresh access token using refresh token"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Change Password",
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"auth": {
					"type": "bearer",
					"bearer": [
						{
							"key": "token",
							"value": "{{accessToken}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"oldPassword\": \"OldPass123!\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewSecurePass456!\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/change-password",
					"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
					"path": ["v1", "auth", "change-password"]
				},
				"description": "Change password (authenticated user)\n\n**Backend Route**: `POST /auth/change-password`\n\n**Authentication**: Required\n\n**Rate Limit**: 100 per minute\n\n**Note**: User must be authenticated with valid access token"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Logout",
			"request": {
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [],
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/logout",
					"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
					"path": ["v1", "auth", "logout"]
				},
				"description": "Logout and invalidate refresh token\n\n**Backend Route**: `GET /auth/logout`\n\n**Note**: Uses GET method (not POST) as per backend implementation"
			},
			"response": []
		}
	]
}
